Another all nighter editing a video. And I am loving it. This episode takes us deep into the cold war that is brewing. Small conflicts are breaking out and full on war is coming. Time to see if my plan is going to work or not.

I also noticed I messed up on my fleet layout, I was suppose to have "4" capital ships not "1" not too sure how I made that mistake. 

Thank you for watching! I enjoy these videos and will continue making them if you keeping coming and watching them. Let me know if you want me to set up a Discord so we can all nerd out over X4, sharing images, mods, stories, experiences, just a fun place for like minded people to hang out.

Thank you for watching! I really appreciate it and thanks for dropping by.

snippet.title: Spooky Spanking Spalooza: VR Horror (Phasmophobia, Layers of Fear, Kobold)
snippet.description:
Tis the Halloween season so I suppose I should toss up something spooky. I hope you enjoy me torturing myself in VR playing some of the scariest games out there. I play Phasmophobia, Layers of Fear, Kobold and one more surprise game at the end. Yes I spent money on the last game, yes I regret much. My steam library shall forever be tainted.

(I realize I spelt disappointed wrong. I should probably stop editing super late at night)

VR is tricky to record in so I apologize for the audio and the jankiness. This was my first time trying it out and I learned a lot. I had loads of fun making this.
